<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <title>
    <%= title %>
  </title>
  <% include ../partials/stylesheet %>
</head>

<body>
  <% include ../partials/header %>
    <div class="jumbotron content">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Do IOT Yourself</h1>
        <p>저희서비스는 일반인들이 쉽게, 이벤트와 그에따른 액션을 연결함으로써 유저 맞춤형 IOT 서비스를 제공하는 플랫폼을 제공하고 있습니다.</p>
        <br><br>
        <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/connect" role="button" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#createPost">Getting Started</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!--modal-->

    <div class="modal fade" id="createPost" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <form action="/home" method="post">
            <div class="modal-header">
              <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
              </button>
              <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Create Connection</h4>
            </div>

            <div class="modal-body">
              <!--
              <fieldset class="form-group">
                <label for="inputitle">Title</label>
                <input type="text" id="inputitle" name="title" class="form-control" placeholder="Comment Title" required="">
              </fieldset>
              <fieldset class="form-group">
                <label for="inputContent">Content</label>
                <textarea id="inputContent" name="content" rows="8" cols="40" class="form-control" placeholder="Comment Description" required=""></textarea>
              </fieldset>
              -->

              <div id="inputaction" class="selectGroup form-control">
                <label for="a-select">Action: </label>
                <select name="iotaction" id="a-select">
                  <optgroup label ="Action">
                    <option>INPUT을 선택하세요.</option>
                    <option>침대누움</option>
                    <option>침대일어남</option>
                    <option>소파앉음</option>
                    <option>소파일어남</option>
                    <option>창문열음</option>
                    <option>창문닫음</option>
                    <option>적외선감지</option>
                    <option>적외선미감지</option>
                  </optgroup>

                </select>

              </div>

              <div id="inputevent" class="selectGroup form-control">
                <label for="e-select">Event: </label>
                <select name="iotevent" id="e-selsect">
                  <optgroup label ="Event">
                    <option>Event를 선택하세요.</option>
                    <option>거실등 ON</option>
                    <option>거실등 OFF</option>
                    <option>스탠드램프 ON</option>
                    <option>스탠드램프 OFF</option>
                    <option>E-mail 전송</option>
                    <option>경보기 ON</option>
                    <option>경보기 OFF</option>
                    <option>환풍기 ON</option>
                    <option>환풍기 OFF</option>

                  </optgroup>

                </select>
              </div>



            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Save changes</button>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr>



    <div class="container">
      <div class="lead">
          <div class="list-group">
          <% connects.forEach(function(connects){ %>
                  <a href="#" class="list-group-item">
                      <div class="connects">
                          <p class="list-group-item-text iotitem"><%= connects.iotaction %> => <%= connects.iotevent %> <%=connects.input_number %><%=connects.output_number %></p>
                      </div>
                  </a>
          <% }); %>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>


    <hr>


    <% include ../partials/footer %>
    <% include ../partials/javascript %>
</body>

</html>
